As I prepare to have my module parse the .fvwm2rc file to find the IconPath
and PixmapPath settings, may I offer a suggestion:

When requesting configuration info (via Send_ConfigInfo), maybe certain well-
defined fvwm parameters get sent, as well. Such as:

* IconPath
* PixmapPath
* ModulePath

for starters, at least. These are parameters that almost *have* to be set,
anyway. Modules should know where to find the same pool of icons and pixmaps
that fvwm is already using, and while a module can look at it's own argv[0] to
find where it lives, it might want to know any other places that modules might
be hanging out.

In the meantime, I'll be parsing the dot-file...

